                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "acquire",
                    "text": "Sounds good!"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "acquire",
            "text": "Pick up a few healthy shrimp from the store. Keep the bag sealed, verify ammonia and nitrite are zero, and float it in your tank for 15 minutes to equalize temperature.",
